{
  "Type": "Standard",
  "Id": "Fk1_5_5",
  "Line": {
    "Id": "Standard",
    "Text": "Anyway, I should not steal all l'attention from you. Where do you come from?"
  },
  "Name": {
    "Id": "Standard",
    "Text": "French Kweebec"
  },
  "UiPage": "Classic_Dialogue.ui",
  "UiFragment": "Classic_Dialogue_Fragment.ui",
  "Choices": [
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "From a boring little town in Middle-of-Nowhere, Emerald Wilds. If you can't tell, my life wasn't a very exciting one.",
      "Action": {
        "Id": "Composite",
        "Actions": [
          {
            "Id": "SetMetadata",
            "MetadataKey": "Fk_Origin",
            "MetadataStore": "FRENCH_KWEEBEC",
            "Metadata": {
              "Id": "String",
              "Value": "Fk_Zone1"
            }
          },
          {
            "Id": "Advance",
            "Next": "Fk1_6A_1"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "My family are nomads in Howling Sands. That kind of environment left me with very little time for anything but survival, so I had to go my own way for the sake of my sanity.",
      "Action": {
        "Id": "Composite",
        "Actions": [
          {
            "Id": "SetMetadata",
            "MetadataKey": "Fk_Origin",
            "MetadataStore": "FRENCH_KWEEBEC",
            "Metadata": {
              "Id": "String",
              "Value": "Fk_Zone2"
            }
          },
          {
            "Id": "Advance",
            "Next": "Fk1_6B_1"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "Spent my whole childhood in Whisperfrost, and boy am I glad that I'm not freezing to death virtually every winter anymore.",
      "Action": {
        "Id": "Composite",
        "Actions": [
          {
            "Id": "SetMetadata",
            "MetadataKey": "Fk_Origin",
            "MetadataStore": "FRENCH_KWEEBEC",
            "Metadata": {
              "Id": "String",
              "Value": "Fk_Zone3"
            }
          },
          {
            "Id": "Advance",
            "Next": "Fk1_6C_1"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "It's complicated. Basically, my great-grandmother is one of the few who survived the collapse of Crucible.",
      "Action": {
        "Id": "Composite",
        "Actions": [
          {
            "Id": "SetMetadata",
            "MetadataKey": "Fk_Origin",
            "MetadataStore": "FRENCH_KWEEBEC",
            "Metadata": {
              "Id": "String",
              "Value": "Fk_Zone4"
            }
          },
          {
            "Id": "Advance",
            "Next": "Fk1_6D_1"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "I don't think I've ever felt tied to a single place. Nothing really stands out.",
      "Action": {
        "Id": "Advance",
        "Next": "Fk1_6E_1"
      }
    },
    {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "I'm a spawn of Varyn himself.",
      "Action": {
        "Id": "Advance",
        "Next": "Fk1_6F_1"
      }
    }
  ]
}